I'm going out with you.''
</P>
<P>
   He told graduating seniors who wouldn't be going on to the
professional ranks to remember the teamwork that led them to
victory. ''what it takes to win on the football team -- hardwork and
discipline and devotion to a common effort -- give you a pretty good
lesson for life.''
